tmpAES1_v = spark.sql( """Select inbndequip_id,
                                inbndequip_number,
                                timeaudit,
                                equipstatus_id,
                                audit_user,
                                audit_log_type                                                                    
From 
	(SELECT                  inbndequip_id,
							 inbndequip_number,
							 timeaudit,
							 equipstatus_id,
							 audit_user,
							 audit_log_type                                             
					  FROM   (SELECT inbndequip_id,
									 inbndequip_number,
									 audit_changed    AS TimeAudit,
									 equipstatus_id,
									 audit_user     AS Audit_User,
									 audit_log_type  ,                               
									 Row_number()
									   OVER (
										 partition BY inbndequip_id, equipstatus_id
										 ORDER BY audit_log_type) AS Position
							  FROM   inbnd_equipment_tbl_audit_equipstatusid)
							 AS TEMP
					  WHERE  position = 1) A """)
tmpAES1_v.createOrReplaceTempView('tmpAES1')
display(tmpAES1_v)

tmpeqpStatus_v = spark.sql("""Select inbndequip_id
      ,container_status
From(
		SELECT inbndequip_id,
		concat_ws(',', collect_list(EquipStatus_Desc)) container_status
		FROM (
			SELECT  ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY E.inbndequip_id ORDER BY E.timeaudit, E.Audit_log_type DESC) AS RNO
				,E.inbndequip_id
				,E.timeaudit
				,ES. EquipStatus_Desc
				,E.audit_log_type                                               
			FROM tmpAES1 E
			Left Join
		comm_equipmentstatus_tbl ES 
		on  ES.EquipStatus_ID= E.equipstatus_id
			ORDER BY RNO
			) A
	
		GROUP BY inbndequip_id
			,RNO 
	) A """)
tmpeqpStatus_v.createOrReplaceTempView('tmpeqpStatus')

display(tmpeqpStatus_v)

tmpinbndContainer_Onwater_QuickClose_v = spark.sql(
"""Select inbndequip_id
From(
select inbndEquip_ID  from (
							select ies.inbndequip_id,ies.audit_changed,
							datediff(MINUTE,ies.audit_changed,lag(ies.audit_changed) over (partition by ies.inbndequip_id order by ies.audit_changed)) as diff,
							row_number() over(partition by ies.inbndequip_id order by ies.audit_changed) as RowNum 
							from inbnd_equipment_tbl_audit_equipstatusid ies
							left join comm_equipmentstatus_tbl es
							on ies.EquipStatus_ID=es.EquipStatus_ID
							where ies.inbndEquip_ID in
							(Select distinct inbndequip_id from tmpeqpStatus where container_status 
							in ('On water,Closed','Closed,On Water')))A
                     where A.RowNum=2 and A.diff<=1
		)A
 """)
tmpinbndContainer_Onwater_QuickClose_v.createOrReplaceTempView('tmpinbndContainer_Onwater_QuickClose')
tmpinbndContainer_Onwater_QuickClose_v.show()

main_result = spark.sql("""SELECT --Cust.Cust_Desc as Customer,
IE.inbndequip_id                      AS Equipment_ID,
IE.inbndequip_number                  AS Container_Number,
IE.cust_id							  AS Customer_ID,
Case when AES.container_status is not null
     then AES.container_status
	 else ESI.EquipStatus_Desc
	 end AS Container_Status,
--MF.Dest_Name AS Facility, 
CHASN.vcshippercountry                AS Origin_Country,
C.country                             AS Origin_Country_Name,
portoforigin                          AS Port_of_Discharge,
--ss.SteamShip_Name as OBL SCAC,
vv.vessel_name + "/" + vv.voyage_name AS Vessel_Voyage,
VV.vesselvoy_id,
IE.vcdischarge                        AS Discharged_Port,
H.harbor_name                         AS Harbor,
OrigDest.dest_id                      AS Original_Destination_ID,
OrigDest.dest_name                    AS Original_Destination, /* Not required due to data sensitivity*/
currentdest_id                        AS Current_Location_ID,
CurrDest.dest_name                    AS Current_Location,
dispatchdest_id                       AS Dispatch_Destination_ID,
DispDest.dest_name                    AS Dispatch_Destination,  /* Not required due to data sensitivity*/
IE.docreceived_fdt                    AS DOC_Rcvd,
IE.asnreceived_fdt                    AS ASN_Received,
--IE.dadreceived_fdt                    AS DAD_Received,
VV.vessel_eta_fdt                     AS ETA,
VV.vessel_ata_fdt                     AS ATA,
IE.dtdischarge                        AS Off_Vessel_Date,
IE.ready_fdt                          AS Ready_Date,
IE.equipallocation_fdt                AS Alloc_Date,
COALESCE(IE.equipeirout_fdt, IE.equipportout_fdt) AS Port_Gate_Out,
IE.equipdispatchin_fdt                AS Dispatch_Date,
--IE.equipportout_fdt                   AS Port_Gate_Out_Old,
--IE.equipeirout_fdt                    AS EIR_Out_PierPass,
IE.equipyardin_fdt                    AS Yard_Gate_In_Date,
IE.equipempty_fdt                     AS Empty_Date,
--IE.equipreload_fdt                    AS Reload_Date,
IE.equipyardout_fdt                   AS Yard_Gate_Out,
--IE.equipdispatchout_fdt               AS Dispatch_Yard_Out,
COALESCE(IE.equipeirin_fdt,IE.equipportin_fdt) AS Port_Gate_In
--IE.equipportin_fdt                    AS Port_Gate_In,
--IE.equipeirin_fdt                     AS EIR_In_PierPass,
--PierPass To Enter the port
--IE.los_dt                             AS LOS_Date
--CPO.[Container PO] AS Container_PO--Kseniia asked to remove this column
--CD.biContainerDistro_ID AS Container_Distro_ID
 from (SELECT * from inbnd_equipment_tbl 
            					where inbndequip_id  not in 
									(Select inbndequip_id from inbnd_equipment_tbl as IE
		                    			LEFT JOIN comm_equipmentstatus_tbl ESI 
                              			ON IE.equipstatus_id = ESI.equipstatus_id  Where ESI.EquipStatus_Desc ='Cancel'
                              		Union 
									Select distinct inbndequip_id from tmpAES1 as AES1
										LEFT JOIN comm_equipmentstatus_tbl ES
										ON AES1.equipstatus_id = ES.equipstatus_id Where ES.EquipStatus_Desc ='Cancel'
									Union
									select inbndEquip_ID from tmpinbndContainer_Onwater_QuickClose
									)
							) AS IE
							JOIN 
							(SELECT Temp.InbndEquip_ID,'' AS vcSHIPPERCountry FROM tmpinbndContainer_DifferentFTS Temp 
							--	UNION SELECT CH.InbndEquip_ID,'' AS ShipperCountry FROM tblFTS_ContainerHeader CH 
							) AS CHASN
					
         ON CHASN.inbndequip_id = IE.inbndequip_id
		 LEFT JOIN comm_country_tbl C 
         ON C.code = CHASN.vcshippercountry
         
		 LEFT JOIN comm_vessel_tbl V 
			ON V.vessel_id = IE.originvessel_id
			 LEFT JOIN comm_equipmentstatus_tbl ESI 
         ON IE.equipstatus_id = ESI.equipstatus_id --AND ESI.EquipStatus_Desc <>'Cancel'
       LEFT JOIN comm_vesselvoy_tbl VV 
         ON VV.vesselvoy_id = V.vesselvoy_id
       LEFT JOIN comm_harbor_tbl H
         ON IE.pickupharbor_id = H.harbor_id
       LEFT JOIN comm_destination_tbl MF 
         ON MF.dest_id = IE.managingfacilitydest_id
       LEFT JOIN comm_destination_tbl CurrDest 
         ON CurrDest.dest_id = IE.currentdest_id
       LEFT JOIN comm_destination_tbl OrigDest 
         ON OrigDest.dest_id = IE.originaldest_id
       LEFT JOIN comm_destination_tbl DispDest 
         ON DispDest.dest_id = IE.dispatchdest_id
       LEFT JOIN comm_customer_tbl Cust 
         ON IE.cust_id = Cust.cust_id --Dropping two records
       LEFT JOIN tmpeqpStatus AS AES
              ON IE.inbndequip_id = AES.inbndequip_id
WHERE  vessel_eta_fdt >= '2018-01-01'


/*and     Case when AES.container_status is not null
											 then AES.container_status
											 else ESI.EquipStatus_Desc
											 end <>'Closed' */
--LEFT JOIN (select inbndEquip_ID,SUBSTRING ((select (', '+rtrim(biContainerPO_ID)) from webfts_hudd.tblFTS_ContainerPO 
--                where inbndEquip_ID = CPO.inbndEquip_ID for xml path ('')),2,1000) as 'Container PO'             
--      from webfts_hudd.tblFTS_ContainerPO CPO
--      group by inbndEquip_ID) AS CPO ON IE.inbndEquip_ID = CPO.inbndEquip_ID
--1,432,383
--AND (c.Code IN ('CN'))
--AND  ( C.code IN ( 'AF', 'AM', 'AZ', 'BH',
--                     'BD', 'BT', 'BN', 'MM',
--                     'KH', 'CN', 'CY', 'GE',
--                     'IN', 'ID', 'IR', 'IL',
--                     'IQ', 'JP', 'JO', 'KZ',
--                     'KW', 'KG', 'LA', 'LB',
--                     'MY', 'MV', 'MN', 'NP',
--                     'KP', 'OM', 'PK', 'PH',
--                     'QA', 'SA', 'SG', 'KR',
--                     'LK', 'SY', 'TJ', 'TH',
--                     'TL', 'TR', 'TM', 'AE',
--                     'UZ', 'VN', 'YE' ,'NULL') )
GROUP  BY IE.inbndequip_id,
          IE.inbndequip_number,
		  IE.cust_id,
		  AES.container_status,
		  ESI.EquipStatus_Desc,
          CHASN.vcshippercountry,
          C.country,
          portoforigin,
          vv.vessel_name,
          vv.voyage_name,
          VV.vesselvoy_id,
          IE.vcdischarge,
          H.harbor_name,
          OrigDest.dest_id,
          OrigDest.dest_name,
          currentdest_id,
          CurrDest.dest_name,
          dispatchdest_id,
          DispDest.dest_name,
          IE.asnreceived_fdt,
          IE.dadreceived_fdt,
          VV.vessel_eta_fdt,
          VV.vessel_ata_fdt,
          asnreceived_fdt,
          IE.docreceived_fdt,
          iE.dtdischarge,
          IE.equipallocation_fdt,
          IE.ready_fdt,
          IE.equipdispatchin_fdt,
          IE.equipeirin_fdt,
          IE.equipeirout_fdt,
          IE.equipportin_fdt,
          IE.equipportout_fdt,
          IE.equipyardin_fdt,
          IE.equipyardout_fdt,
          IE.equipempty_fdt,
          IE.equipreload_fdt,
          IE.equipdispatchout_fdt,
          IE.los_dt
--order by VV.vessel_eta_fdt desc


    
	  
			 """)
display(main_result)
